Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.85,0:00:03.85,op,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.50,0:04:00.08,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}許せば進めるし　恨みは立ち止らす
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.08,0:04:05.08,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}あれは僕のせいにしな　それも僕のせいにしてよ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.08,0:04:10.20,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}君をずっと立ち止める　その全てと
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.20,0:04:15.92,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}僕以外を許して　進んで行きなよ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.31,0:04:25.36,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}生涯枯れることのない花　と名付けても
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.36,0:04:30.47,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}生涯枯れることのない花　になることはない
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.01,0:04:35.58,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\3c&HDA7B00&}真面目に生きていれば　いつか報われる
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.04,0:04:40.62,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}そうやって言い切ってしまえば　それは嘘になる
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.62,0:04:45.69,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}身に起こるその数十％　自業自得でも
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.69,0:04:50.60,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}残りの数％　誰のせいでもないその不平等
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.60,0:05:00.68,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\3c&H1200FF&\t(2560,2810,\3c&H265CF5&)\t(3269,3519,\3c&HDA7B00&)\t(3603,3811,\3c&H47C73E&)\t(3937,4103,\3c&H5F2558&)\t(4437,4562,\3c&H386A2D&)\t(5396,5438,\3c&H1200FF&)\t(6189,6481,\3c&H45B6FE&,\bord0.8)\t(8274,8441,\blur0,\3c&H103568&,\bord2,\1c&HCCE1F4&)\t(8775,9275,\3c&H52164B&)\t(9359,9609,\blur3,\3c&H103568&)}一番いけないことはさ　自分はダメだと思うこと
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.68,0:05:05.68,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}あれは僕のせいにしな　それも僕のせいにしてよ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.68,0:05:10.72,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}僕以外を許して進んで行きなよ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.72,0:05:16.29,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}君自身のことも許してあげてよ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.72,0:05:16.29,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.50,0:04:00.08,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}宽恕促人前行 仇恨让人停滞
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.08,0:04:05.08,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}把那个当成我的错吧 把这个也归咎于我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.08,0:04:10.20,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}原谅让你一直停滞不前之事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.20,0:04:15.92,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}原谅除我以外的所有人 前进吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.31,0:04:25.36,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}即便取名为永不凋谢之花
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.36,0:04:30.47,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}也无法永不凋谢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.01,0:04:35.58,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\3c&HDA7B00&}认真活着就会有回报
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.04,0:04:40.62,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}如此断言的话语必定是谎言
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.62,0:04:45.69,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}百分之几十是自作自受
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.69,0:04:50.60,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}剩下的百分之几不怨任何人 如此不公
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.60,0:05:00.68,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\3c&H1200FF&\t(2560,2810,\3c&H265CF5&)\t(3269,3519,\3c&HDA7B00&)\t(3603,3811,\3c&H47C73E&)\t(3937,4103,\3c&H5F2558&)\t(4437,4562,\3c&H386A2D&)\t(5396,5438,\3c&H1200FF&)\t(6189,6481,\3c&H45B6FE&,\bord0.8)\t(8274,8441,\blur0,\3c&H103568&,\bord2,\1c&HCCE1F4&)\t(8775,9275,\3c&H52164B&)\t(9359,9609,\blur3,\3c&H103568&)}最糟糕的 是自我否定
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.68,0:05:05.68,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}把那个当成我的错吧 把这个也归咎于我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.68,0:05:10.72,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}原谅除我以外的所有人 前进吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.72,0:05:16.29,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}也原谅你自己吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.29,0:05:18.29,op-cn,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.79,0:22:38.08,ed-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}そうじゃない　求めるものは
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.08,0:22:42.63,ed-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}強くこの手で掴もう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.72,0:22:55.27,ed-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}泣いたって変わらないなら
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.27,0:23:01.94,ed-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}笑っても同じ　そう思っていた
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.94,0:23:08.57,ed-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}大事なものが守れないのは
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.57,0:23:15.54,ed-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}弱い僕のせい　そう思っていた
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.54,0:23:21.25,ed-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}どうして？　いま　ここに僕がいる理由は
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.25,0:23:24.66,ed-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}誰が解らなくてもいい
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.66,0:23:28.30,ed-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}そう　君がいれば
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.30,0:23:35.06,ed-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}見境無く燃える焔　 群衆が指をさす
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.06,0:23:38.77,ed-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}僕はきっと強くなって　
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.77,0:23:41.69,ed-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}誰だって守り抜く
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.10,0:23:45.07,ed-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\c&HB54E25&\3c&HFFFFFF&}愛したいひとを想い　
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.07,0:23:49.78,ed-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\c&HB54E25&\3c&HFFFFFF&}闇をこの手で払おう
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.79,0:22:38.08,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不是这样 追求之物
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.08,0:22:42.63,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要亲手去紧握
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.72,0:22:55.27,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一味哭泣 则无法改变
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.27,0:23:01.94,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}强颜欢笑也一样 我如此想到
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.94,0:23:08.57,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}无法保护珍视之人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.57,0:23:15.54,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是因为我太弱小 我如此想到
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.54,0:23:21.25,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}为什么？ 我会在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.25,0:23:24.66,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}无人知晓也无妨
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.66,0:23:28.30,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}只要有你在身旁
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.30,0:23:35.06,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}燃尽万物的烈焰 饱受非议
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.06,0:23:38.77,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我一定要变强
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.77,0:23:41.69,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}保护所有人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.10,0:23:45.07,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\c&HB54E25&\3c&HFFFFFF&\b1}心怀所爱之人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.07,0:23:49.78,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\c&HB54E25&\3c&HFFFFFF&\b1}亲手驱散黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.78,0:23:51.78,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.19,0:00:07.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}站 站住
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.18,0:00:11.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}拜托你了 奥村
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.58,0:00:16.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}希望你能用降魔剑打倒不净王
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.53,0:00:20.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我知道这是个无理又勉强的请求
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.95,0:00:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}但是如果 如果你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.50,0:00:28.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}能像你父亲那样对我施以些许慈悲之心
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.48,0:00:31.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我想将希望寄托于你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.75,0:00:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}谢谢你看到最后 胜吕达摩
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.04,0:00:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}和我想的一样 真是不得了的内容啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.20,0:00:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}但是 虽然对不住胜吕同学的父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.82,0:00:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}哥哥的火焰对不净王是否有效还只是推测
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.02,0:00:56.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不能因为这种不确切的事使用降魔剑
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.03,0:00:59.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}燐 这封信是写给你的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.38,0:01:01.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你想怎么做
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.68,0:01:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.09,0:01:07.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}修拉小姐 你怎么能问他呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.65,0:01:10.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我 我想帮他
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.93,0:01:14.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}哥哥 你知道自己现在的处境吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.65,0:01:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我也被老头子救了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.55,0:01:24.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}所以 如果我能派上用场 那我也想去战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.08,0:01:25.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不过
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.06,0:01:28.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}当然 这只是我个人的意愿
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.06,0:01:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那就要驳回你的请求…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.04,0:01:30.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好 我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.71,0:01:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}降临于此 回归于彼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.08,0:01:38.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}修拉小姐 你要做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.05,0:01:39.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}还能做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.60,0:01:44.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}他说要战斗 但不清楚他的状态我可没法批准
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.08,0:01:46.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}就在这里拔出来试试
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.10,0:01:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}修拉小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.25,0:01:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}哥哥才刚刚放出火焰胡闹了一番
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.72,0:01:55.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}现在把降魔剑给他太不理智了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.39,0:01:58.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}要是再发生点什么 肯定会被处刑的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.51,0:01:59.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.12,0:02:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我咏唱禁锢咒的时候梵蒂冈就已经知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.38,0:02:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}他们现在随时都可能以此为由处决他
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.36,0:02:10.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}现在害怕也已经晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.12,0:02:11.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}而且这样没关系吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.92,0:02:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}如果不净王复活 出现在了这个世界上
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.80,0:02:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}现在它就比燐更危险
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.30,0:02:23.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}而且你也见过那么多次了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.69,0:02:26.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}他的火焰对目前为止遇到的恶魔都有效
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.70,0:02:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}值得一试
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.31,0:02:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}燐 你拔出来试试
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.04,0:02:44.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.03,0:02:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}哥哥 你在做什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.79,0:02:52.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.51,0:02:54.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}拔不出来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.08,0:02:56.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.83,0:02:58.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不 不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.92,0:03:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不知怎么回事 完全拔不出来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.45,0:03:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那我来帮你拔吧 给我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.64,0:03:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我自己拔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.12,0:03:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}大概是哪里卡住了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.07,0:03:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}对 肯定是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.76,0:03:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.51,0:03:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.14,0:03:17.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}燐 你害怕了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.68,0:03:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不过这也很正常
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.19,0:03:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}刚刚才因为掌握了火焰而欣喜若狂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.11,0:03:30.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}然而转瞬之间又回到了原点 你是这样的心情对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.04,0:03:35.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}要是再拔出这把剑 我会怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.06,0:03:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}也许又会发狂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.82,0:03:41.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这次说不定真的会伤到其他人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.93,0:03:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这种事…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.34,0:03:44.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我说中了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.91,0:03:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你完全失去自信了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.75,0:05:25.55,biaoti,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fax-0.15\fad(0,518)\3c&HC4732D&\bord1.5\pos(1072,605)}气焰万丈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.98,0:05:23.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}等 等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.46,0:05:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}会因为这种事拔不出剑吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.70,0:05:29.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}哥哥 把剑还回来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.10,0:05:32.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这可真是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.10,0:05:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}晚上好 三位
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.99,0:05:39.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}菲雷斯卿
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.97,0:05:42.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}梅菲斯特 你来干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.38,0:05:45.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这问法还真是没礼貌啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.51,0:05:49.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我时隔已久的登场居然是在监狱里 我才失望呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.04,0:05:53.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}真是的 亏我还是来给你们收拾烂摊子的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.96,0:05:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}1 2 3
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.88,0:06:01.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fnArial}Das stärkste Gefängnis
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.77,0:06:05.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}防御力最高的牢房
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.54,0:06:12.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}梵蒂冈本部联系我了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.24,0:06:15.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}因方才咏唱禁锢咒之事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.33,0:06:18.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}经三贤者座下的审问委员会投票决定
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.85,0:06:21.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}处决奥村燐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.80,0:06:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}等 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.55,0:06:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}动作真快 这是真的假的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.84,0:06:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}都这种时候了 我可没这闲工夫跑过来撒谎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.06,0:06:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}雪男 你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.65,0:06:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}比起这些事情 讨伐不净王才是当务之急
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.25,0:06:47.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不好意思 能帮我拿一下这个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.97,0:06:49.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你怎么连这个都知道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.62,0:06:51.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}既然这么了解就来帮忙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.92,0:06:53.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.67,0:06:56.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不行的 我不擅长对付脏东西
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.99,0:06:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}会过敏的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.65,0:07:00.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我的鼻子已经…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.83,0:07:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不净王复活后会迅速成长
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.36,0:07:10.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}待它完全成熟之时 京都将化为一座死城
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.75,0:07:14.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我正带着蝮赶回外派所 马上就到了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.27,0:07:16.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}请尽量让大家都到门口来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.20,0:07:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你们那边能看见吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.81,0:07:21.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}能看见吗 蟒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.89,0:07:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那就是不净王吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.63,0:07:30.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}讨伐不净王需要不少人手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.59,0:07:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}虽然只是些简易的装备
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.10,0:07:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我就送给你们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.43,0:07:39.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}希望这个能派上用场
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.58,0:07:44.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那么 祝各位好运
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.76,0:07:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}喂 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.79,0:07:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那个混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.58,0:07:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}总之 我们先做力所能及的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.32,0:07:53.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.76,0:07:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我们应该也会被召集去讨伐不净王
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.71,0:08:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}外派所让我们紧急集合
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.05,0:08:07.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}能动的人都去外派所
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.16,0:08:07.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.40,0:08:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}怎么回事 外面好吵啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.65,0:08:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是不是发生什么事了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.09,0:08:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我听说抓住蝮了 是真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.94,0:08:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是的 柔造正带她回来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.66,0:08:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}抓住蝮了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.43,0:08:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}少住持
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.38,0:08:26.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}柔造回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.16,0:08:27.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}蝮 柔造
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.01,0:08:36.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}谢谢你把大家召集来了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.62,0:08:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}大家 我是个叛徒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.86,0:08:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}但是 还请大家听我说几句话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.17,0:08:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}就在刚才 我和藤堂三郎太
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.74,0:08:57.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}用夺来的右眼和左眼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.69,0:09:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}复活了不净王
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.92,0:09:02.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不净王？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.24,0:09:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不净王不是江户时代就被打倒了的恶魔吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.80,0:09:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}它一直以假死状态被封印在金刚深山的地下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.45,0:09:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}安静点
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.62,0:09:20.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}现在明陀宗座主胜吕达摩大人 正留在那里孤军奋战
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.71,0:09:28.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}请各位施以援手 打败不净王
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.66,0:09:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}真 真是任性
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.72,0:09:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}明明你自己把它复活的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.95,0:09:34.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}再说了 不净王到底是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.76,0:09:36.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}要怎么打倒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.64,0:09:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}现在不是议论这些事的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.64,0:09:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}驱魔队全体 巡逻一队和二队 以及深部一队
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.67,0:09:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}出发讨伐不净王
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.92,0:09:49.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不净王是腐之王的眷属
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.45,0:09:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}全员接种疫苗以抵抗瘴气
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.21,0:09:53.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}快去做接种疫苗的准备
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.58,0:09:54.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.49,0:09:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}蝮
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.75,0:10:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}龙 龙士大人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.39,0:10:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你的右眼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.39,0:10:05.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.58,0:10:11.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}请救救他 救救住持大人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.83,0:10:15.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}少住持 我带她去医务室
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.40,0:10:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}柔造 你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.72,0:10:21.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我稍后去和一队汇合
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.52,0:10:24.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}少住持请务必和驱魔塾的各位一起回旅馆
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.75,0:10:25.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}廉造 子猫
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.89,0:10:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}给我好好保护少住持
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.71,0:10:29.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}要是他出了什么事 你们就等死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.34,0:10:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好好 交给我们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.40,0:10:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不用管我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.83,0:10:38.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}快去救住持大人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.50,0:10:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.65,0:10:50.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}她可是女人啊 藤堂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.79,0:10:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}少住持 这也没办法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.92,0:10:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}柔哥都那样说了 我们就待在旅馆吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.24,0:10:58.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.44,0:10:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你们过来一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.30,0:11:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}雾隐老师
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.06,0:11:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}由于刚才放出了火焰 燐的处刑决定了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.31,0:11:11.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这是梵蒂冈的决定 无法违抗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.53,0:11:12.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}然后
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.80,0:11:16.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}胜吕同学 这个暂时给你保管
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.36,0:11:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}俱利伽罗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.89,0:11:23.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}还有你父亲给燐的信
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.45,0:11:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}他说打倒不净王需要燐的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.75,0:11:29.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}燐是想帮忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.19,0:11:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你们能把他救出来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.94,0:11:37.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}想让燐免除处刑 就只能让他将功赎罪了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.52,0:11:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}把这些迷彩斗篷拿去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.85,0:11:42.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}有隐身效果
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.22,0:11:46.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}应该能不被看守发现 接近他的牢房
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.19,0:11:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}雾隐队长 请快一点
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.61,0:11:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.81,0:11:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}就是这样 说到底我也只是骑士团的狗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.88,0:11:55.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不能擅自行动
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.64,0:11:59.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}交给你们了 一切由你们自己判断
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.16,0:12:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我们去救燐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.89,0:12:13.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那个
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.83,0:12:16.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}虽然很想去救他
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.29,0:12:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}但这样我们就是和梵蒂冈作对了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.44,0:12:23.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}但 但是如果就这样袖手旁观 再也见不到燐了的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.01,0:12:25.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}大家一定会后悔的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.07,0:12:35.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}牢房在这边吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.86,0:12:36.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}少住持
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.73,0:12:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}胜吕同学 谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.48,0:12:42.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}子猫 你在开玩笑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.19,0:12:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}三轮同学
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.15,0:12:46.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我必须保护少住持
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.81,0:12:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}而且 我也一定会后悔的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.50,0:12:55.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}怎么这样 你就这么怕柔哥吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.39,0:13:00.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}怎么连出云都这样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.97,0:13:01.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}神木同学
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.97,0:13:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}大家都怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.06,0:13:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}会死的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.27,0:13:07.76,zhu,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}别挡路廉造
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.20,0:13:10.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}小鬼回旅馆睡觉去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.72,0:13:15.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我作为明陀的男人 死也要死得轰轰烈烈
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.81,0:13:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.83,0:13:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}又是明陀又是后悔的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.53,0:13:22.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我真的不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.01,0:13:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}真是的 麻烦死了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.17,0:13:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}痛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.80,0:13:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你刚才说话了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.89,0:13:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}没有 是你说的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.78,0:13:38.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我什么都没说啊 是你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.12,0:13:40.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你少骗人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.00,0:13:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}吓死我了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.40,0:13:45.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}都怪子猫踩到我的脚了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.59,0:13:47.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}原谅我吧 志摩
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.66,0:13:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这个斗篷虽然很厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.68,0:13:52.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}但是看不到对方也很麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.48,0:13:54.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}应该就在前面
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.20,0:13:57.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是那扇门吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.60,0:14:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}本大爷是{\fnArial}Das stärkste Gefängnis {\r\blur2}防御力最高的牢房
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.86,0:14:10.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不过
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.62,0:14:14.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}虽然我无法从里面被打开 但从外面就很容易
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.75,0:14:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那么问题来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.32,0:14:18.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这是什么角色
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.61,0:14:19.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}恶魔？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.63,0:14:22.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}为什么说我防御力最高呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.92,0:14:25.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}来攻击本大爷试试吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.12,0:14:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}只能上了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.32,0:14:41.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}答案是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.96,0:14:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我能定住对本大爷抱有敌意的人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.33,0:14:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这就是本大爷名字的由来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.66,0:14:53.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}怎么会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.26,0:14:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}可为什么我没事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.09,0:15:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}因为你没有敌意
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.22,0:15:02.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你很弱也没拿武器
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.99,0:15:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}没有了小尼 我真的一无是处
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.48,0:15:12.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}但是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.31,0:15:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}如果燐就这样死了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.68,0:15:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我绝对不要这样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.65,0:15:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}从外面可以打开门吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.93,0:15:30.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}当然可以 不过你就出不来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.84,0:15:33.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}就算是为了大家 我也必须救出燐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.24,0:15:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这是什么地方
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.37,0:15:48.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我不能死在这种地方
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.92,0:15:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我不能死
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.34,0:15:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}真的是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.15,0:16:02.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你会老实等着被骑士团杀掉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.75,0:16:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}对了 还有自杀这个选项哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.73,0:16:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你死了算了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.75,0:16:14.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不能让大家救我的努力白费
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.89,0:16:16.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我一直是这么想的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.02,0:16:19.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}但是 说不定…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.82,0:16:22.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}要是再拔出这把剑 我会怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.22,0:16:26.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这次说不定真的会伤到其他人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.56,0:16:31.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我真的应该去死
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.34,0:16:35.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}还什么忙都没帮上 就要死掉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.27,0:16:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}到头来 连跟大家和好都做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.64,0:16:43.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我到底是为什么被救下来的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.94,0:16:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}老头子 为什么要救我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.00,0:16:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.56,0:16:54.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}燐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.57,0:16:56.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}诗惠美
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.96,0:17:00.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}燐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.48,0:17:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我来救你了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.19,0:17:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}雾隐老师把事情都告诉我们了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.74,0:17:16.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我们会和你一起战斗的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.76,0:17:18.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}快点从这里出去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.38,0:17:23.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}别过来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.85,0:17:26.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.38,0:17:31.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我没信心能控制住火焰
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.53,0:17:37.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我一直觉得可以靠气势来解决一切
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.87,0:17:40.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}但这好像行不通
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.48,0:17:42.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我就这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.15,0:17:47.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}死了比较好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.32,0:17:48.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}什…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.61,0:17:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你在说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.65,0:17:53.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不准再说这种话了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.74,0:17:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.61,0:17:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}也不用懂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.17,0:18:03.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}别这样 别这样笑着疏远我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.94,0:18:07.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我很想帮你的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.58,0:18:14.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你走吧 我是怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.27,0:18:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}一点都不烫
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.65,0:18:26.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好温暖
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.49,0:18:36.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我真傻
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.11,0:18:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}只想着自己
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.13,0:18:43.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}从没认真关注过燐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.30,0:18:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这样还算什么朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.18,0:18:59.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}燐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.33,0:19:02.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.56,0:19:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}笨 笨蛋 你…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.57,0:19:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}危险
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.72,0:19:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.74,0:19:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你看 我根本就没有被烧伤
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.52,0:19:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是你保护了我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.00,0:19:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}所以没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.40,0:19:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你不怕我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.94,0:19:29.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不怕
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.06,0:19:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是 是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.44,0:19:41.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}奥村同学
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.36,0:19:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}大家都是来救我的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.59,0:19:49.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我 我不想让你死掉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.28,0:19:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}只要知道你没有危险 我就会跟你和好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.20,0:19:55.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}子猫丸
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.78,0:19:57.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我先声明
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.25,0:20:00.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我只是听从了雾隐老师的指示罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.07,0:20:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.78,0:20:04.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我可是很不想来的 表扬我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.57,0:20:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}大 大家
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.43,0:20:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}总之谢谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.39,0:20:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}胜吕… 同学
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.99,0:20:19.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}和老爸吵架的事确实是我不够冷静
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.30,0:20:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你说得没错 仅限和老爸吵架的事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.20,0:20:28.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这是战斗要用的吧 拿着
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.60,0:20:33.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我 我才是 打了你对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.70,0:20:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我带你去金刚深山
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.24,0:20:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}之后要怎样随你便
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.65,0:20:42.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我要用我的方式战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.38,0:20:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}胜吕
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.60,0:20:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}相信我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.94,0:20:48.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}虽然身为撒旦之子的事实无法改变
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.56,0:20:50.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}但我一定会把火焰控制好给你看
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.92,0:20:53.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}所以 相信我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.11,0:20:55.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那种事情怎样都无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.28,0:20:58.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我之所以不能原谅你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.55,0:21:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是因为你把这些事全都闷在心里
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.26,0:21:04.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}什么都不跟我们说
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.47,0:21:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你要我怎么相信你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.53,0:21:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}难道只有我一个人觉得我们是同伴吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.80,0:21:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不 不是的 我不是那个意思
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.15,0:21:15.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}等等 就是因为这个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.12,0:21:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你生气就只是因为这个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.33,0:21:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这原因真新颖
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.24,0:21:21.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}志摩
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.23,0:21:23.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}胜吕
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.47,0:21:27.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这样啊 我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.28,0:21:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那么 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.74,0:21:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}舞台和演员终于齐了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.73,0:21:39.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好了 就让我尽情欣赏这场战斗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.89,0:21:50.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}大家听好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.10,0:21:53.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}目标是洛北的金刚深山
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.41,0:21:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}去打倒不净王
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.99,0:22:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我只能用接下来的行动证明自己
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.79,0:24:06.34,zhu,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}第八集 父子相传
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.77,0:24:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我是自愿选择现在这条路的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.04,0:24:11.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}跟爸爸和哥哥无关
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.89,0:24:13.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}
